707770f-a.title: Manhattan: 2nd Ave. - 7th St.
707770f-a.text:
(1)
Second Avenue, east side, north from 7th Street, showing buildings on the west side at St. Mark's Place (8th Street).
April 2, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
(2)
The same, not showing the west side below 11th Street.
June 25, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
